   "## Concept: Trajectories and batch\n",
   "\n",
   "Export sessions to ShareGPT-style JSONL for training pipelines.\n",
   "\n",
   "**Harness Agent** implements this subsystem in ``trajectories/export.py``. External harnesses differ in scale (tool count, platforms) but share the same architectural slot.\n",
   "\n",
   "| Concern | Harness Agent | Hermes (reference) | OpenClaw (reference) |\n",
   "|---------|---------------|--------------------|----------------------|\n",
   "| This chapter | ``trajectories/export.py`` | see architecture docs | workspace/gateway docs |\n",
   "| Entry point | `AIAgent` or CLI | `run_agent.py` / gateway | gateway + workspace |\n"
  ]
 },
 {
  "cell_type": "markdown",
  "metadata": {},
  "source": [
   "## How it works\n",
   "\n",
   "`export_trajectories()` reads SQLite, writes JSONL.\n",
